    "body": "I've added some logging to the angular digest cycle.\nEvery --------- is a digest cycle\nI output every watch that is dirty or that gets clean.\n\n![image](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1710840/17573314/703b4208-5f0e-11e6-8d00-020b3d6c0458.png)\n\nIt seems that some services start initializing in the [http-server](https://www.npmjs.com/package/http-server) version, but not in electron.\n"
